      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and still runs like a dream! It\u2019s in really nice shape\u2014well-loved and looked after, with just the usual character you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s seen some fun adventures. Perfect for someone who wants a solid, smooth drive without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin, you'll love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
