    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound Nissan 300ZX Twin Turbo featuring the legendary VG30DETT power plant. This Z32 chassis retains its factory Garrett T22 turbochargers, delivering linear boost across the rev range. Power is managed via a crisp 5-speed manual transmission and a viscous limited-slip differential. The Super HICAS rear-steering system remains fully operational, ensuring precise turn-in and lateral stability. Recent service includes a timing belt replacement and refreshed vacuum lines to maintain peak manifold pressure. This is a driver-focused example with a clean undercarriage and robust compression across all six cylinders.",
      "price": 34500.0,
