    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss luster, showing only the minor, expected signs of road use that come with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept smoke-free; the seating surfaces are firm and free of tears, while the dashboard and electronics\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the car has been serviced regularly, with a recent oil change, new air filters, and a comprehensive brake service just completed. It starts reliably, idles smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. Whether you are commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car offers a tight, responsive driving experience and a quiet cabin. It is a dependable, honest vehicle that is ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
